messages.message: imo we should say our final piece here and shut it down, but do it in a way that allows us to take the higher ground so we can win their business back later once we have an account manager for them

if you’re standing in a pile of stinging ants and they’re biting your feet, you can spend all day trying to squash each one, or you can walk away from the pile and figure out how to deal with the whole pile (or if it even matters)
